      "questions": [
        {
          "text": "<p>Kako se kaže \"His email is...\" u neformalnom razgovoru na španskom?</p>",
          "distractors": [
            "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Su correo electrónico es...</span></p>",
            "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Su número es...</span></p>",
            "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Su usuario es...</span></p>"
          ],
          "answer": "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Su correo es...</span></p>"
        },
        {
          "text": "<p>Kako se kaže \"His/Her name is...\" na španskom?</p>",
          "distractors": [
            "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Se vive...</span></p>",
            "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Se tiene...</span></p>",
            "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Se trabaja...</span></p>"
          ],
          "answer": "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Se llama...</span></p>"
        },
        {
          "text": "<p>Ako želiš da pitaš „What is his profession?”, koju reč bi trebalo da koristiš za pitanje?</p>",
          "distractors": [
            "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Cómo...?</span></p>",
            "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Dónde...?</span></p>",
            "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Quién...?</span></p>"
          ],
          "answer": "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Cuál...?</span></p>"
        },
        {
          "text": "<p>Izaberite ispravan način da kažete „broj telefona“ na španski.</p>",
          "distractors": [
            "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Número de correo</span></p>",
            "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Correo de número</span></p>",
            "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Teléfono de número</span></p>"
          ],
          "answer": "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Número de teléfono</span></p>"
        },
        {
          "text": "<p>Koji glagol bi koristio/koristila da kažete \"On radi u kompaniji\"?</p>",
          "distractors": [
            "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Come</span></p>",
            "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Vive</span></p>",
            "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Es</span></p>"
          ],
          "answer": "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Trabaja</span></p>"
        },
        {
          "text": "<p>Koja je zvanična reč za \"email\" na španskom?</p>",
          "distractors": [
            "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Corréo</span></p>",
            "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Correo</span></p>",
            "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Correo electronico</span></p>"
          ],
          "answer": "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Correo electrónico</span></p>"
        },
        {
          "text": "<p>Kako se kaže \"Korisničko ime je...\" na španski?</p>",
          "distractors": [
            "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Su correo es...</span></p>",
            "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Su número es...</span></p>",
            "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Su colega es...</span></p>"
          ],
          "answer": "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Su usuario es...</span></p>"
        },
        {
          "text": "<p>Kako se pita \"Gde si from?\" na španski?</p>",
          "distractors": [
            "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿De qué eres?</span></p>",
            "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿De cuál eres?</span></p>",
            "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿De cómo eres?</span></p>"
          ],
          "answer": "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿De dónde eres?</span></p>"
        },
        {
          "text": "<p>Koji je tačan način da se napiše ova rečenica na španskom?</p>",
          "distractors": [
            "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">El es mi colega.</span></p>",
            "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">El mi colega.</span></p>",
            "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Es él colega.</span></p>"
          ],
          "answer": "<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Él es mi colega.</span></p>"
        },
        {
          "text": "<p>Izaberite opciju koja NE PRISTUPA odgovarajućem znaku i reči na španski.</p>",
